All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildSurveyController
    Controller class that connects the app to an instance of BuildSurveyView when user prompts for a new Survey object to be created.
    BuildSurveyView
    View class that creates the GUI of the window that appears when a user chooses to make a new survey.
    Question
    Question class is a wrapper for a question on a survey.
    ResponseDatabaseHelper
    This class connects to a database to persist response data between runs of the app.
    Survey
    This class wraps a list of questions into a survey it stores a list of Question objects and a title.
    SurveyDatabaseHelper
    This class connects to a database to persist survey data between runs of the app.
    SurveyResultController
    This class is a controller for the SurveyResultView.
    SurveyResultView
    This class is the view for viewing a survey result.
    TabbedPaneController
    handles all actions involved with the tabbed panes
    TabbedPaneView
    sets up GUI for all the tabs which appear at the top of the screen Extends JFrame and uses BorderLayouts and TabbedPanes to format the view
    TakeSurveyController
    handles all actions the user performs in the take survey screen
    TakeSurveyView
    sets up the GUI for the take survey screen Extends JFrame and uses BoxLayouts, BorderLayouts, and ScrollPanes to format the view components
